WEBVTT

00:00:06.463 --> 00:00:08.002
U kasnom 17. stoljeću

00:00:08.002 --> 00:00:11.762
student medicine imena Johannes Hofer
primjetio je čudnu bolest

00:00:11.762 --> 00:00:15.593
koja je pogodila švicarske plaćenike
na radu u inozemstvu.

00:00:15.593 --> 00:00:16.622
Simptomi,

00:00:16.622 --> 00:00:17.534
uključujući umor,

00:00:17.534 --> 00:00:18.573
nesanicu,

00:00:18.573 --> 00:00:19.902
nepravilan rad srca,

00:00:19.902 --> 00:00:21.223
probleme s probavom,

00:00:21.223 --> 00:00:23.334
i vrućicu bili su tako snažni,

00:00:23.334 --> 00:00:26.513
da su vojnici morali biti otpušteni.

00:00:26.513 --> 00:00:30.445
Hofer je otkrio, uzrok nije bio
fizička bolest,